{
  "stem": "20800.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "By 5 o'clock, we out, because an hour was walking to the factory where we were working.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So it was a very hardship, so sometimes we didn't feel to wash it and go have particularly in winter.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we have just knock them and see-- and hope for the best.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, we got a lot of casualties from sickness, and that's where I come, because my friend was in, in this-- she was a sister and revered.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's how we call it in the factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a-- how you-- sanitary [? quarter. ?] If you have somebody sick, I rang her, and she was making sure that she get a place in the hospital, because we-- the hospital was where we lived.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On the factory, it somebody sort of have some sort of cut or bruise or something, so it was done by the factory sanitary sister.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But hospital was in the quarters where we lived, special block.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We start-- by about April, late of April, there-- we knew that we will be getting away from there because Russians start to be very close, and they didn't want Russian to come to this factory.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what they decided to [? recreate ?] the whole camp from there up north.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- they start to prepare the whole camp to walk out to north Rostock.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember, Rostock.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was north, much north, from the, from the place that we had that's working camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it's happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, boy, the march.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, I think it's in April, because by Seder of 1945, I ran away from the walk.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The walk was prepared by [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a lot of SS men, women and men, a lot of dogs.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
